skdetail:

Invocation Name: prime number
des: A prime number (or a prime) is a natural number greater than 1 that cannot be formed by multiplying two smaller natural numbers. By enabling this skill, Alexa can give you result of the input number, weather its a PRIME number or NOT. Example of prime numbers are 1, 2, 3, 5, 7, ..... 19........ 100799 ... and so on....
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
